Many Many Thanks Kentucky-Kid activated using the browser option to get the id for key gen

to kraut58
after installing program run it. you will be given a choice to try, buy, activate. Click on activate. On the next window to open select to activate via browser. At this point your browser should open up with the id which should be a long list of numbers. . Run keygen as admin copy and paste the id into the key gen hit generate. copy and paste the generated code below the id in the browser. hit activate.Done
